This class expands the :class:`.jet_builder` class parameters with
    further fields useful in the fitting.
    Each :class:'par' instance is charge to update accordingly 
    the values in the :class:`par`  instance and in the 
    corresponding member of the :class:`jet_builder` instance
    
      
    
    Public Members
    
    :ivar name:  parameter name
     
    :ivar val_start: parameter starting value
     
    :ivar val: parameter current value
     
    :ivar val_last_call: parameter value in the last call
     
    :ivar val_min: parameter minimun value
      
    :ivar val_max: parameter maximum value
     
    :ivar frozen: (boolean) , if the parameter if frozen
     
    :ivar log: (boolean), if the parameter is in logarithmic scale
     
    :ivar best_fit_val: parameter best-fit value
     
    :ivar best_fit_err: parameter best-fit error
    
    
    
    
    :func:`.minimizer.fit_SED`
    :attr:`.mod.class.attr`